
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Happiness in the Digital Age</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
    font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
    background:#0a0a0a;
    color:#ffffff;
    height:100vh;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    overflow:hidden;
    position:relative;
}

/* Background Glow */
body::before{
    content:'';
    position:absolute;
    width:800px;
    height:800px;
    background:radial-gradient(circle,
    rgba(0,255,194,0.15) 0%,
    rgba(0,255,194,0.05) 30%,
    transparent 70%);
    filter:blur(50px);
    z-index:0;
}

.container{
    position:relative;
    z-index:1;
    text-align:center;
    max-width:900px;
    padding:40px;
}

.logo{
    font-size:14px;
    letter-spacing:6px;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:#00FFC2;
    margin-bottom:30px;
}

h1{
    font-size:clamp(3rem,8vw,6rem);
    font-weight:700;
    line-height:1;
    margin-bottom:25px;
}

.highlight{
    color:#00FFC2;
}

p{
    font-size:1.2rem;
    color:#b5b5b5;
    max-width:650px;
    margin:0 auto 40px;
    line-height:1.8;
}

.soon{
    display:inline-block;
    padding:14px 34px;
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    border-radius:999px;
    font-size:14px;
    letter-spacing:4px;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
}

footer{
    position:absolute;
    bottom:30px;
    width:100%;
    text-align:center;
    color:#666;
    font-size:12px;
    letter-spacing:2px;
}

@media(max-width:768px){
    p{
        font-size:1rem;
    }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

    <div class="logo">
        Happiness in the Digital Age
    </div>

    <h1>
        Rediscover <span class="highlight">Meaning</span><br>
        in a Connected World
    </h1>

    <p>
        Exploring happiness, technology, human connection,
        and the future of well-being in the digital age.
        A new documentary experience is coming soon.
    </p>

    <div class="soon">
        Coming Soon
    </div>

</div>

<footer>
    © 2026 • Happiness in the Digital Age
</footer>

</body>
</html>
